718980f-b.title: Manhattan: Claremont Avenue - 122nd Street (West)
718980f-b.text:
(1)
Claremont Ave., at and adjoining the N.E. corner of West 122nd
Street, as seen from the east side of Riverside Drive, and across
park between these streets. Buildings shown, house the Institute of
Musical Art.
1936.
Walter L. Bogert.
(2)
A view eastward on the north side of Wast 122nd Street, and showing
the afore mentioned institute.
1936.
Walter L. Bogert.
(3)
Broadway, west side, at West 122nd Street, and showing the Insti-
tute of Musical Art, at the N.E. corner of Claremont Ave, a street which
parallels Broadway.
1936.
Walter L. Bogert.
